## Goal
- Build LibWise, a web-based Library ERP system with book management, borrower management, borrowing/returns, fines, availability tracking, and reports.

## Constraints & Preferences
- Tech stack: ASP.NET Core MVC (C#) on .NET 8, MySQL via XAMPP, Entity Framework Core (Pomelo 8.0.0), Bootstrap 5 frontend, no REST API (templates only).
- Barcode scanner uses keyboard-wedge mode (inputs into text fields).
- Three roles: Admin, Librarian, Assistant Librarian (AL). AL logs into their own account to tag each transaction.
- Database: `libwise` on localhost:3306, user root, no password.

