## Critical Context
- App runs at `http://localhost:5111`. Default credentials: `admin@libwise.com` / `Admin123!`.
- MySQL connection string: `Server=localhost;Port=3306;Database=libwise;User=root;Password=;`.
- AL barcode workflow: scan borrower barcode → system looks up/fetches borrower → AL processes transaction → `BorrowedByUserId` / `ReturnedByUserId` records the AL who handled it.
- Fine calculation: overdue days × `DailyFineRate` (PHP 5), capped at `MaxFine` (PHP 500). Calculated at return time.

